BRAND NEW ARC! PERFECT JUMPING-ON POINT FOR NEW READERS!
The second round of the ultimate deathmatch begins here -- which fan-favorite characters are on a collision course, and what does last month's shocking reveal mean for The Rat and Manchurian? The mysteries grow deeper and the casualty list grows longer as DEATHMATCH continues!
